request.description:
**Verifikasi via tinker bahwa refund record dan wallet credit dibuat:**

```bash
docker compose exec app php artisan tinker
```

```php
$p = App\Models\Payment::find(PAYMENT_ID); // ganti PAYMENT_ID

// Cek refund record
$refund = $p->refund()->latest()->first();
echo 'Refund created: ' . ($refund ? 'YES' : 'NO') . PHP_EOL;
echo 'Refund amount: ' . $refund?->amount . PHP_EOL;
echo 'Refund reason: ' . $refund?->reason . PHP_EOL;

// Cek wallet credit
$user = $p->order->user;
$walletTx = $user->walletTransactions()->latest()->first();
echo 'Wallet credit: ' . ($walletTx ? 'YES' : 'NO') . PHP_EOL;
echo 'Credit type: '   . $walletTx?->type . PHP_EOL;    // harus: credit
echo 'Credit amount: ' . $walletTx?->amount . PHP_EOL;  // harus: sesuai payment amount
```

**Juga cek log:**
```bash
docker compose exec app grep 'Double payment detected' storage/logs/laravel.log | tail -5
```
